      "content": "The decision isn't about personal preference; it's about accuracy and ethics. The audit showed that your model consistently undervalues candidates from certain minority backgrounds, creating a feedback loop that favors specific demographics. If your goal is to identify the highest probability of success, why should we believe that a human-led committee is an \"irrational\" step forward?",
